snippet.title: Untitled Princess Peach Game - Teaser | Nintendo Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the very brief teaser for an untitled Princess Peach Game. Showcasing 2D platforming and outfit changes for the royalty of the Mushroom Kingdom. 

#IGN #Nintendo
